title: StemmerKuchl
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, International, Organic, Take-out, German, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Soup bar offering usually 3 vegan soups each day. Examples might be: regional vegetables with pot barley, Thai carrot coco ginger, oriental tomato curry with rice. All bread and salads are organic and vegan. Also offers vegan pesto, vegan bolognese, and vegan ice cream. Specials like vegan sausages from time to time. Located in the oldest farm in Munich, yet central in the Sendling district.
